                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400511-1516-offence-1 t18400511-cd-182"></join>21st of April</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of John Bowers, from his per<lb></lb>son.—2nd <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNT</hi>, stating it to be the goods of a man whose name is un<lb></lb>know.</rs>
